commit.message: Add: Tests for --edges-only and --edge-threshold options
Refactor: Parameterise default edge_threshold
Add: Check to make sure --edge-threshold is passed if --edges-only is
Add: man page entries for new --edge-threshold and --edges-only options
Add: Prevent autocomplete from adding space after options like --height=
Add: Bash autocompletion for --edge-threshold and --edges-only options
Refactor: Simplify and comment gradient direction character selection
Add: Use edges-only option to suppress non-edge output
Add: edges-only option to print edges only
Refactor: remove unnececssary check on when to draw edges
Bugfix: Correct image bounds clamping in get_pixel_index function
Bugfix: Corrected gradient kernels array size
Add: Shade edges with gradient above edge_threshold using directional characters /|\=
Refactor: use curLinePos to keep track of line pos in ASCII mode and variable charaxter width mode in print_image_no_colors
Add: Functions to get the direction and magnitude of a vec2
Add: Function to calculate image gradient
Add: New command line option --edge-threshold
Refactor: Use memcpy to copy characters rather than loop in print_image_colors
Refactor: Use memcpy to copy characters rather than loop in print_image_no_colors
Add: Function get_pixel_index and refactor and simplify image flipping logic
